# English-Only Content

This project currently supports only English. When adding or editing content:

- Use English for all user-facing strings (UI labels, buttons, errors, toasts).
- Use English for comments and documentation in the codebase.
- Avoid adding non-English copy or translations.

## Examples

```typescript
// BAD: non-English UI copy
toast.error("Erreur de sauvegarde");

// GOOD: English-only UI copy
toast.error("Save failed.");
```
